rob a tree of its strength.

3
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:50,120
Sailing with
the current of the ocean

4
00:03:50,170 --> 00:03:52,120
does not insult a sea vessel.

5
00:04:01,170 --> 00:04:04,120
Surrendering my weapons to you

6
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:06,210
is not an insult to me.

7
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:09,080
In fact, it is an honour

8
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:11,310
brother Yudhishthir.

9
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,310
I have a feeling that

10
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:25,110
when it comes to strength
and military strategies

11
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:27,150
you are superior to me.

12
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:40,080
